00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:51,000
If you can command troops in the frontline,

280
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:53,710
the heavenly generals and soldiers

281
00:18:53,710 --> 00:18:56,680
will definitely be more loyal to Your Majesty.

282
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,750
I see.

283
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,170
You should be leaving.

284
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:00,460
Yes.

285
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,240
Kuang Lu,

286
00:19:06,860 --> 00:19:08,060
you should also be leaving.

287
00:19:08,460 --> 00:19:09,880
I need to think carefully

288
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:12,640
how to deal with it.

289
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,000
Yes.

290
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,370
Your Majesty.

291
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:33,040
Water Immortal is anxiously
longing for Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir.

292
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:35,260
It is God’s will whether she can get it or not.

293
00:19:36,020 --> 00:19:37,570
But as Leader Yin Que said,

294
00:19:38,420 --> 00:19:40,280
if Fire Immortal’s soul is still alive,

295
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:41,750
with Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir,

296
00:19:42,370 --> 00:19:43,390
he might be reborn.

297
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,060
Then…

298
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:47,710
I speak without thinking.

299
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,350
Please punish me.

300
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,680
When did I ask you to kneel?

301
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,370
Stand up.

302
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,330
Thank you, Your Majesty.

303
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:12,910
Your Majesty.

304
00:20:13,080 --> 00:20:14,150
What’s the matter?

305
00:20:15,220 --> 00:20:17,440
The dethroned Heavenly Empress
jumped off Linyuan Tower.

306
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:19,170
Leave.

307
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,150
And,

308
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:23,130
Water Immortal seems to be seriously injured

309
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:24,910
and fainted just now.

310
00:20:43,970 --> 00:20:44,770
Why?

311
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:46,770
I don’t know either.

312
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:48,370
The Light of Xuanqiong

313
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:51,970
actually needs to be borne
by Water Immortal’s body.

314
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:53,970
Due to the strong light,

315
00:20:53,970 --> 00:20:55,840
I’m afraid her body has been melted.

316
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:59,000
Even if you help her with magic power,

317
00:20:59,220 --> 00:21:03,220
I’m afraid she can only stay alive for some time.

318
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,770
You should be leaving.

319
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:09,930
Yes.

320
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:36,860
Mi,

321
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:40,110
I will find the way to save you.

322
00:22:18,540 --> 00:22:20,420
"Mengtuo Scripture"

323
00:22:23,130 --> 00:22:24,200
Blood Ball.

324
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:26,640
Change fate against God’s will.

325
00:22:53,930 --> 00:22:54,510
Mi,

326
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:57,570
since you are my inexorable doom,

327
00:22:58,680 --> 00:22:59,530
now

328
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:02,330
I come to accept it.

329
00:24:03,530 --> 00:24:04,460
Your Majesty,

330
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,530
what are you doing?

331
00:24:08,020 --> 00:24:08,950
Leave!

332
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,420
Your Majesty,

333
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:12,860
now the demon army is about to attack.

334
00:24:13,570 --> 00:24:14,640
If you hurt yourself,

335
00:24:14,860 --> 00:24:15,620
how can Heaven Realm...

336
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:19,260
how can Heaven Realm win them?

337
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:21,220
If I don’t save her now,

338
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:23,620
it’ll be too late.

339
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:24,910
Your Majesty!

340
00:24:24,910 --> 00:24:25,800
Leave!

341
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:06,020
Are you really going to
fight for King of Gu City?

342
00:25:06,550 --> 00:25:07,930
I’m not fighting for him,

343
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:09,800
but for Feng, for Demon Realm

344
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:10,910
and for this grudge.

345
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:12,020
If it is for Demon Realm,

346
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:13,710
you should consider

347
00:25:13,930 --> 00:25:16,370
what consequences this war will bring.

348
00:25:16,950 --> 00:25:17,840
Your father is right.

349
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:19,970
You really shouldn’t act on impulse

350
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:20,910
for Fire Immortal.

351
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:22,730
But I have promised to fight this war,

352
00:25:23,130 --> 00:25:24,280
I can’t have cold feet.

353
00:25:24,730 --> 00:25:26,680
There can be no turning back now.

354
00:25:27,170 --> 00:25:27,880
Princess.

355
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:28,820
Stop.

356
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:29,880
Xu Feng died distressingly,

357
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:31,260
and Heavenly Emperor is so arrogant.

358
00:25:31,620 --> 00:25:33,260
My father actually submits to humiliation.

359
00:25:34,060 --> 00:25:35,570
Though I don’t want to irritate him,

360
00:25:36,020 --> 00:25:38,370
I really can’t bear this.

361
00:25:39,660 --> 00:25:41,400
If you are not willing to fight with me,

362
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,550
I won’t force you.

363
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:49,480
In fact, you know I don’t mean that.

364
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:50,550
No matter what happens,

365
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:52,460
I will share weal and woe with you.

366
00:26:23,930 --> 00:26:24,640
Your Majesty.

367
00:26:29,530 --> 00:26:30,330
I am fine.

368
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:43,220
Your Majesty.

369
00:26:43,750 --> 00:26:44,680
Did you use…

370
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,080
Do not let Jin Mi know this.

371
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,680
But…

372
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:50,600
This is a forbidden magic of Heaven Realm.

373
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:53,400
I am Heavenly Emperor.

374
00:26:54,770 --> 00:26:56,550
If this matter is known by others,

375
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:58,280
I’m afraid there will be
changes in the six realms,

376
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:01,660
and Mi will be gossiped

377
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,640
by others.

378
00:27:05,930 --> 00:27:06,860
Remember.

379
00:27:08,910 --> 00:27:11,170
Do not let others know this.

380
00:27:12,150 --> 00:27:12,910
Understand?

381
00:27:14,150 --> 00:27:15,310
I understand.

382
00:27:18,770 --> 00:27:19,440
Your Majesty.

383
00:27:22,060 --> 00:27:24,460
Drink this bowl of decoction
to nourish your body.

384
00:27:49,040 --> 00:27:49,750
Phoenix.

385
00:27:51,530 --> 00:27:52,510
Phoenix.

386
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,680
Phoenix.

387
00:28:01,170 --> 00:28:03,310
Water Immortal, you are awake.

388
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:06,600
Kuang Lu, what happened?

389
00:28:07,530 --> 00:28:08,120
Yesterday,

390
00:28:08,120 --> 00:28:10,950
you injected the Light of
Xuanqiong into Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir.

391
00:28:11,750 --> 00:28:14,330
You were injured as
you couldn’t bear the strength

392
00:28:14,770 --> 00:28:15,570
of the Light of Xuanqiong.

393
00:28:16,730 --> 00:28:17,710
Luckily, His Majesty,

394
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,440
His Majesty

395
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,600
transferred some magic power to you

396
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:22,550
and thus saved you.

397
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,730
You can recover in a few days.

398
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:27,350
His Majesty transferred
some magic power to me?

399
00:28:28,330 --> 00:28:29,440
How is he now?

400
00:28:30,510 --> 00:28:31,570
His Majesty is fine.

401
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:33,350
Just now immortals have things to report,

402
00:28:33,710 --> 00:28:35,310
so he is occupied now.

403
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:36,770
He will come to see you some time later.

404
00:28:39,930 --> 00:28:41,040
Have a cup of tea.

405
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:42,860
Thanks.

406
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:45,260
Immortal,

407
00:28:47,170 --> 00:28:48,330
can you keep

408
00:28:49,620 --> 00:28:51,000
the next conversations

409
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:52,330
between you and me?

410
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,800
Go ahead.

411
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:57,400
Is your heart

412
00:28:58,860 --> 00:29:00,060
made of ice?

413
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,220
Even if it is made of ice,

414
00:29:04,860 --> 00:29:08,200
as His Majesty paid for you time and time again,

415
00:29:08,730 --> 00:29:10,550
your heart should have melted.

416
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:15,750
Immortal,

417
00:29:16,330 --> 00:29:17,480
I beg you.

418
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:18,680
I beg you

419
00:29:18,950 --> 00:29:20,600
to show more feelings for His Majesty, OK?

420
00:29:21,220 --> 00:29:23,310
You can lie to him or temporize.

421
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:25,530
It will be better than

422
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:29,400
make him sad

423
00:29:30,910 --> 00:29:32,640
and bitterly disappointed day and night.

424
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:36,200
I have feelings for His Majesty,

425
00:29:38,020 --> 00:29:39,800
but that’s not what he wants.

426
00:29:40,770 --> 00:29:42,640
If I lie to him or temporize,

427
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,510
pretending to love him very much,

428
00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:48,240
that will hurt him more.

429
00:29:48,910 --> 00:29:49,800
Just like you.

430
00:29:50,370 --> 00:29:52,370
If I ask you to pretend

431
00:29:54,110 --> 00:29:55,880
to be indifferent to His Majesty,

432
00:29:56,370 --> 00:29:57,530
can you do it?

433
00:30:01,530 --> 00:30:02,910
Why did you say so?

434
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,310
His Majesty is so distinguished

435
00:30:05,710 --> 00:30:07,620
that I can never think of that.

436
00:30:07,930 --> 00:30:08,820
Kuang Lu,

437
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,370
take it easy.

438
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:11,970
I don’t mean to blame you.

439
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:13,840
In fact,

440
00:30:15,130 --> 00:30:16,420
you and I are the same.

441
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:19,220
We both know in heart

442
00:30:19,570 --> 00:30:21,080
we can’t be with the ones we love,

443
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,530
but we can’t cheat our hearts.

444
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:28,770
I promise you.

445
00:30:29,170 --> 00:30:30,730
No one else

446
00:30:31,350 --> 00:30:33,930
will know our conversations today.

447
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:35,660
Don’t worry.

448
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:38,730
Thank you, Water Immortal.

449
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:40,860
I’ll be leaving.

450
00:30:49,750 --> 00:30:51,970
Yesterday, I was injured
by the Light of Xuanqionge,

451
00:30:53,130 --> 00:30:54,550
but I am fine today.

452
00:30:54,910 --> 00:30:56,730
How can I recover so fast?

453
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,970
What is your color?

454
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:18,110
Your Majesty.

455
00:31:18,860 --> 00:31:19,710
Has she woken up?

456
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:21,440
I told her that

457
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,110
Your Majesty was fine and
had gone to discuss matters with others,

458
00:31:24,820 --> 00:31:27,440
and would go to see her later.

459
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:37,000
Your Majesty,

460
00:31:37,930 --> 00:31:41,040
Blood Ball will consume half of your life.

461
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:43,000
Is it worthy

462
00:31:43,530 --> 00:31:44,770
to do this?

463
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:50,370
Has Immortal Tai Si joined with Lord Po Jun?

464
00:31:52,910 --> 00:31:53,620
OK.

465
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:56,330
Tell him

466
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,020
once the war begins,

467
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,330
I will show up.

468
00:32:00,950 --> 00:32:01,800
Your Majesty,

469
00:32:02,370 --> 00:32:03,750
you are weak now

470
00:32:04,110 --> 00:32:05,310
and need rest.

471
00:32:05,970 --> 00:32:07,350
If you go to the battlefield now,

472
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:09,880
it’ll be too dangerous.

473
00:32:10,770 --> 00:32:12,330
Since I took this position,

474
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:15,710
I have to be responsible for Heaven Realm.

475
00:32:17,750 --> 00:32:18,330
Your Majesty.

476
00:32:44,460 --> 00:32:45,750
Supreme Lord Lao.

477
00:32:49,570 --> 00:32:50,860
Water Immortal.

478
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:54,680
Yesterday, you almost died yesterday.

479
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:58,730
How can you recover so fast?

480
00:33:00,370 --> 00:33:01,530
I almost died?

481
00:33:02,330 --> 00:33:03,170
So serious?

482
00:33:04,060 --> 00:33:07,350
Do you have any elixir to cure me?

483
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:08,600
Water Immortal,

484
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:10,550
I don’t have any elixir

485
00:33:10,820 --> 00:33:13,350
to heal the injury caused
by the Light of Xuanqiong.

486
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:16,640
Is there any other way?

487
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:20,730
What do you think of?

488
00:33:21,260 --> 00:33:22,910
In ancient times,

489
00:33:22,910 --> 00:33:25,130
there was a book called Mengtuo Scripture

490
00:33:25,350 --> 00:33:27,170
in which all kinds of
forbidden magic are recorded.

491
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,970
I seem to hear of

492
00:33:30,770 --> 00:33:33,170
a kind of magic named Blood Ball

493
00:33:33,750 --> 00:33:35,219
which can change fate.

494
00:33:35,750 --> 00:33:36,679
But…

495
00:33:36,679 --> 00:33:37,710
But what?

496
00:33:38,239 --> 00:33:41,880
According to the book,

497
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:43,929
the rescuer needs to
cut seven sinews and vessels

498
00:33:44,770 --> 00:33:46,909
to inject half essence in his body

499
00:33:46,909 --> 00:33:48,510
into the blood

500
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:50,150
to make Blood Ball

501
00:33:50,730 --> 00:33:51,620
to feed the injured.

502
00:33:52,150 --> 00:33:53,710
The rescuer

503
00:33:53,710 --> 00:33:57,570
will consume half of his life.

504
00:34:31,130 --> 00:34:31,620
Mi.

505
00:34:34,640 --> 00:34:36,110
You seldom come to my room.

506
00:34:37,620 --> 00:34:38,770
What do you come here for?

507
00:34:48,240 --> 00:34:49,570
Have you ever heard of

508
00:34:50,420 --> 00:34:51,880
the magic Blood Ball?

509
00:34:52,550 --> 00:34:53,660
If you didn’t make Blood Ball,

510
00:34:54,460 --> 00:34:55,660
how would you be injured,

511
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:58,770
and how would I be safe?

512
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:02,280
That’s not true.

513
00:35:02,910 --> 00:35:04,200
Where did you hear this?

514
00:35:05,130 --> 00:35:06,950
No one will use such
evil magic in Heaven Realm.

515
00:35:07,750 --> 00:35:09,040
You were not seriously injured yesterday.

516
00:35:09,750 --> 00:35:11,350
I just transferred some magic power to you.

517
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:13,350
OK.

518
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:14,770
Since you don’t admit it,

519
00:35:15,260 --> 00:35:17,170
I’m going to call Immortal Qihuang.

520
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:18,150
Mi.

521
00:35:20,640 --> 00:35:21,970
Are you insane?

522
00:35:22,150 --> 00:35:23,530
Do you know

523
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:25,710
you will consume half of your life by doing so?

524
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:26,770
If you died,

525
00:35:27,530 --> 00:35:28,510
I would go insane.

526
00:35:30,770 --> 00:35:33,440
Blood Ball is the forbidden magic
recorded in Mengtuo Scripture.

527
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,350
There is Dream Changing Magic.

528
00:35:36,020 --> 00:35:37,080
There is also Blood Ball.

529
00:35:37,970 --> 00:35:40,150
Did you never read Mengtuo Scripture?

530
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:41,880
Do you doubt

531
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:44,950
I made you misunderstand Xu Feng?

532
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:48,600
Even if there was someone playing a trick,

533
00:35:50,060 --> 00:35:51,000
it must be the one

534
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,770
who killed your father.

535
00:35:59,080 --> 00:35:59,880
Mi,

536
00:36:02,060 --> 00:36:03,350
I didn’t know Blood Ball

537
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,200
is also the forbidden magic
recorded in Mengtuo Scripture.

538
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:08,240
After my mother died,

539
00:36:08,910 --> 00:36:10,200
I brought some remains of hers

540
00:36:10,600 --> 00:36:12,330
to Heaven Realm from Dongting Lake.

541
00:36:12,770 --> 00:36:14,020
Blood Ball

542
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:16,600
is a kind of magic recorded by my mother.

543
00:36:17,620 --> 00:36:18,770
I didn’t know whether it was true.

544
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,510
You were in danger,

545
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,640
so I had to have a try.

546
00:36:25,750 --> 00:36:26,910
Even if I died,

547
00:36:28,550 --> 00:36:30,200
it was a worthy death.

548
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:33,840
Back then, Lord Puchi saved me,

549
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,530
and I paid him back with 1,000 years of magic power.

550
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,280
Now,

551
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:43,970
you have given me half of your life.

552
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,840
How can I pay you back?

553
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:49,350
I don’t need that.

554
00:36:53,570 --> 00:36:54,510
Mi,

555
00:36:55,040 --> 00:36:56,510
as long as I can watch you

556
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:59,040
and be at your side,

557
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:00,950
that is enough.

558
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,280
In the past, I had the whole night sky,

559
00:37:04,820 --> 00:37:06,550
but I still felt lonely.

560
00:37:08,330 --> 00:37:09,840
Now I have you,

561
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:12,860
so I feel content.

562
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:17,080
Mi,

563
00:37:18,110 --> 00:37:21,800
I only hope you can be carefree

564
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,440
and happy as before.

565
00:37:25,620 --> 00:37:26,370
